On Tue, 20 Sep 2005, Dave C. Bolen wrote:

> Are the Bosch ones *really*, *really* worth it...especially considering
> you have to order the bulbs separately?

You only buy the lens/reflector once and it's yours for life!

The high quality lens/reflector will produce a much sharper pattern than
the cheaper versions.  The sealing and reflector plating will also be
better.
